xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2605:\"<p><span class=\'embed-youtube\' style=\'text-align:center; display: block;\'><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'520\' height=\'323\' src=\'http://www.youtube.com/embed/5FQ08S6roF8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' frameborder=\'0\'></iframe></span></p>\n<p>Lyrics:</p>\n<p>Back in 05, the InvestorGeeks blog.<br />\nUsing WordPress, it was a memory hog.<br />\nDay jobbing .NET. Life was hard.<br />\nNow I’m growing an empire&#8230; and living it large. </p>\n<p>[chorus]<br />\nWordPress. With a capital P.<br />\nMad themes, CPTs since version 3.<br />\nThe best CMS, it will make your cream.<br />\nBlogging my life. Living the dream.</p>\n<p>You say Drupal. So uncool.<br />\nI&#8217;d rock Twenty Ten if I wanted to go old school.<br />\nI used to use the Kubrick theme. LEGIT.<br />\nOne menu, a sidebar, and that was it.</p>\n<p>Back then, I was hacking the core.<br />\nLike going to war. But not anymore.<br />\nAnother upgrade just broke my shit.<br />\nGood thing I learned plugins or I’d have quit.</p>\n<p>[chorus]<br />\nWordPress. With a capital P.<br />\nMad themes, CPTs since version 3.<br />\nThe best CMS, it will make your cream.<br />\nBlogging my life. Living the dream.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;m spitting for sages.<br />\nYou haven&#8217;t updated in ages.<br />\nYour menu&#8217;s still using wp_list_pages.<br />\nDon’t have the haters.</p>\n<p>Hate the obfuscators.<br />\nThe code dictators. The weak creators.<br />\nMe, I want the code to be free.<br />\nI’m a GPL crusader and always will be.</p>\n<p>[chorus]<br />\nWordPress. With a capital P.<br />\nMad themes, CPTs since version 3.<br />\nThe best CMS, it will make your cream.<br />\nBlogging my life. Living the dream.</p>\n<p>My rhymes will leave you sated,<br />\nwhile yours so bad they been deprecated.<br />\nSince 2.9, I’m keeping the rhyme<br />\nas I read below the more line.</p>\n<p>I make my girl weep<br />\nwhen I do_action beneath the sheets.<br />\nI clean all my inputs with stripslashes_deep().<br />\nNot suvblte.</p>\n<p>WordPress hits you over your head.<br />\nFills you with the spirit of Matt Mullenweg.<br />\nNot bitter. Never a quitter.<br />\nI follow PhotoMatt’s dinners on Twitter.</p>\n<p>[chorus]<br />\nWordPress. With a capital P.<br />\nMad themes, CPTs since version 3.<br />\nThe best CMS, it will make your cream.<br />\nBlogging my life. Living the dream.</p>\n<p>[chorus]<br />\nWordPress. With a capital P.<br />\nMad themes, CPTs since version 3.<br />\nThe best CMS, it will make your cream.<br />\nBlogging my life. Living the dream.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/2012/10/the-wordpress-rap/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n			\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Mistake #2: Playing Designer\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"http://www.paidmembershipspro.com/2012/10/mistake-2-playing-designer/\";s:7:\"a